Pokemon Go

Introduction:
  - Hellos
  josh: We are here to tell you about our brand new video game, Pokemon GO, coming to stores next year.
  If you want to spend every day of ur life in ur mom's basement till ur 26, THIS IS THE GAME FOR YOU.
Whats so special about this game?
   Parakh : The game follows the main character, on his/her journey to catch every pokemon in the region. Along the way the main character has the
      ability to choose different joinable teams, obviously catch different pokemon, and try to catch them all. 
    : The player is dropped into a route just outside of the player's home town. Where the main character learns everything they need to know 
      about the adventure that they are about to go on form the professor.
    : From there the player has the ability to explore the route trying to catch all the pokemon that exist in the region. 
     
Technical features
 Chris & Luke: Menu
    : Shoots pokeballs on spacebar
    : Walking animations for main characters
    : Sound
    : Help menu
    : Menu to view all of the caught pokemon
